    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯计划将 4 月份海运柴油出口量降至 5 个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/russia-plans-to-cut-diesel-export-by-sea-in-april-to-5-month-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在乌克兰无人机袭击炼油厂和季节性维护大幅降低原油加工率后，俄罗斯计划将 4 月份西方主要港口的每日柴油出口量降至五个月以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/russia-plans-to-cut-diesel-export-by-sea-in-april-to-5-month-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 09:50:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
